data.description: Build your dream home at this great location. Rare building opportunity in Denver. Less than one mile from City Park. On bus routes to downtown. Blocks away from great establishments like The Plimoth and NOLA Voodoo Tavern and Perks. Minutes away from all that RINO has to offer. Property sold as is with the structure on it as a scrape. Schedule your personal showing today! This Property is vacant and the structure (shown in pictures) has been demolished.
